export function latitudeToTile(lat, zoom) {
return Math.floor(latitudeToWebMercator(lat, zoom));
}

export function longitudeToTile(lng, zoom) {
return Math.floor(longitudeToWebMercator(lng, zoom));

// Determine the tile row for a given latitude
export function latitudeToWebMercator(lat, zoom) {
const rads = toRadians(lat);
const log = Math.log(Math.tan(rads) + 1 / Math.cos(rads));
return Math.floor(((1 - log / Math.PI) / 2) * 2 ** zoom);
return ((1 - log / Math.PI) / 2) * 2 ** zoom;
}

export function longitudeToWebMercator(lng, zoom) {
return (2 ** zoom) * ((lng + 180) / 360);
}

// Determine the latitude of the center of the tile row
function tileToLatitude(y, zoom) {
export function tileToLatitude(y, zoom) {
const n = Math.PI - 2 * Math.PI * (y / (2 ** zoom));
return ((180 / Math.PI) * Math.atan(0.5 * (Math.exp(n) - Math.exp(-n))));
}

getScale({ zoom }: { zoom?: number; } = {}) {

}

setMaxZoom() {
const { height, width, xMax, xMin, yMax, yMin } = this;
let maxZoom = 20;
let scale = this.getScale({ zoom: maxZoom });

if (this.markers.length < 2) {
return;
}

while (
longitudeToTile(xMax, maxZoom) - longitudeToTile(xMin, maxZoom) > 2
|| latitudeToTile(yMax, maxZoom) - latitudeToTile(yMin, maxZoom) > 2
|| width * scale.x <= Math.abs(xMax - xMin)
|| height * scale.y <= Math.abs(yMax - yMin)
) {
maxZoom--;
scale = this.getScale({ zoom: maxZoom });
if (maxZoom === 3) {
break;
}
}

if (this.zoom > maxZoom) {
this.scale = scale;
this.zoom = maxZoom;
}
}
